1108,695,TOX21_ARE_BLA_Agonist_ch1,1,1,"Data from the assay component TOX21_ARE_BLA_Agonist_ch1 was analyzed into 1 assay endpoint. This assay endpoint, TOX21_ARE_BLA_Agonist_ch1, was analyzed in the negative fitting direction relative to DMSO as the negative control and baseline of activity.
